data.description: Built in 2022, this new construction home offers a 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom, 2-car garage concrete block and stucco house. This home is perfect for large families seeking a peaceful environment. It features a layout that provides privacy with separate formal and informal spaces. The kitchen boasts upgraded 36-inch wood cabinetry with crown molding, 6-inch pulls, upgraded wood pattern vinyl flooring, and stainless steel appliances. The master bathroom includes a separate tub and tiled shower. Conveniently situated near shopping, schools, and restaurants.
